OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FEnvironment Agency figures released in
OL,7,FMarch showed storm overflows spilt
OL,8,Fsewage into England's rivers, lakes
OL,9,Fand coasts for a record of more than
OL,10,F3.61 million hours over 464,056
OL,11,Fdischarges in 2024.
OL,13,FThis was the first full year that 100%
OL,14,Fof storm overflows had been monitored
OL,15,Fand the figures revealed that although
OL,16,Fthe number of spills fell slightly
OL,17,Fcompared with 2023, the duration of
OL,18,Fsewage discharges was up.
