OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FThese spills should only take place in
OL,7,F"exceptional circumstances" to prevent
OL,8,Fsewers from being overwhelmed in heavy
OL,9,Frainfall and backing up into homes.
OL,11,FA survey for SAS suggests that more
OL,12,Fthan a quarter of adults in England
OL,13,F(27%) have considered withholding
OL,14,Fwater bill payments due to anger with
OL,15,Fthe actions of their suppliers.
OL,17,FJust one-third of respondents believe
OL,18,Fthat their water supplier will take
OL,19,Fthe necessary action to end sewage
OL,20,Fpollution.
