OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FSAS said it received 1,853 sickness
OL,7,Freports through its Safer Seas &
OL,8,FRivers Service app last year ` an
OL,9,Faverage of five people a day.
OL,11,FAround 331 people had to see a doctor,
OL,12,Fwith 79% of them reporting that their
OL,13,Fdoctor had attributed their illness to
OL,14,Fsewage pollution.
OL,16,FAll of this comes as households in
OL,17,FEngland and Wales face an annual water
OL,18,Fbill increase of an average of #123
OL,19,Fthis year, as firms face accusations
OL,20,Fof years of underinvestment in their
OL,21,Fcrumbling infrastructure.
