OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FIn February, the government brought in
OL,7,Fthe Water (Special Measures) Act 2025
OL,8,Fin efforts to clamp down on these
OL,9,Fpractices. The new legislation
OL,10,Fprovides powers for Ofwat to ban the
OL,11,Fpayment of bonuses to water bosses if
OL,12,Fthey fail to meet high environmental
OL,13,Fstandards.
OL,15,FThe law also creates new penalties
OL,16,Fincluding possible imprisonment for
OL,17,Fexecutives who break the law by
OL,18,Fallowing pollution.
